Name: The Little Tank Hunter
About the game: ABOUT THE GAME Your mission is to destroy the tank master, can you do it? Shoot yourself through various levels and collect coins. Be careful, if you die you lose some of them. Find the hidden emeralds and use them to upgrade your tank skills. Unlock different tank skins. Test you skills in the Endless mode. Remix Mode same levels, but harder and slightly different. FEATURES 60 levels 7 bonus levels 5 boss fights endles mode remix mode 14 tank skins 5 over worlds 2 side quest 4 different difficulty levels 'easy, normal, hard and impossible'
